    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Great news for buyers looking for a reliable, well-maintained ride \u2014 this one is in good condition and ready to go! It runs well and presents nicely, with the kind of everyday dependability you can count on. There's normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a great driving experience. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just looking for a trustworthy daily driver, this car delivers solid value at a fair price. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, suitable for everyday reliable transportation. The exterior shows visible wear, including minor dents, light scratches, and some areas where the paint has faded or chipped \u2014 nothing unusual for a car of this age and use, but worth noting for buyers expecting a pristine appearance. The interior is functional with normal signs of use: some scuffing on the seats, minor wear on high-touch surfaces, and a couple of small stains on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts consistently, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. There are no major mechanical issues, though as with any used vehicle at this price point, routine maintenance and minor repairs may be needed over time. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is an honest, practical vehicle for a buyer who prioritizes function over flawless aesthetics.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in mint condition, and we are proud to offer one of the finest examples you will find on the market. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint is deep, vibrant, and free of scratches, dents, chips, or fading. Every panel is straight and true, with chrome and trim pieces looking factory-fresh. The interior is equally impressive: all seating surfaces, carpets, headliner, and dashboard are in pristine shape with no tears, stains, or wear to speak of. All electronics, controls, and comfort features function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes, suspension, and mechanical systems are all in top-notch working order. Service records are available and reflect consistent, careful maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. If you are looking for a vehicle you can drive with complete confidence from day one, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Solid & Sensible \u2013 A Practical Pick at an Honest Price! \ud83d\ude99\n\nNeed a car that gets the job done without breaking the bank? This one's worth a look! We'll be upfront with you: this vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, and it'll serve you well as everyday transportation. There are some signs of wear and minor cosmetic imperfections that come with its age and use, but nothing that gets in the way of reliable daily driving. It's not a showroom queen, but it's a genuine, road-ready vehicle priced to reflect exactly what it is. Great for commuters, second-car shoppers, or anyone who values function over flash. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll appreciate the honest value here!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're proud to provide an honest, thorough description for prospective buyers. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains good gloss and color consistency, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns to report. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with seats showing modest wear but no tears, stains, or damage. All major controls, electronics, and comfort features are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. The vehicle has been regularly maintained and is ready for daily driving without the need for immediate repairs. This is a solid, dependable car that offers real value for a buyer looking for a trustworthy used vehicle.",
      "price": 32000.0,
